I see the composers are Muslims the singer is Hindu the arrangements done by Christians and Sikhs that’s beautiful. 😍
To make it more interesting as an Afghan I see Afghanistan’s culture and heritage i🇦🇫 involved in this master piece too.
Sufism in particular (طریقه چشتیه) Tareghaa Chashteya is from my city Herat, 🇦🇫this is the one type where you can add music and instruments. 

Love to all !
